OL,3,CBenjamin Zephaniah: Late Birmingham
OL,4,Clegend first to receive city honour
OL,6,FThe late birmingham poet, writer and
OL,7,Factor Benjamin Zephaniah will be the
OL,8,Ffirst person to receive the City of
OL,9,FBirmingham Medal.
OL,11,FBorn and raised in Handsworth,
OL,12,FZephaniah went on to become one of
OL,13,FBritain's best-loved poets.
OL,15,FHe helped put the city on the cultural
OL,16,Fmap through his work, which often
OL,17,Faddressed themes such as racism,
OL,18,Finequality and human rights.
