OL,3,CBenjamin Zephaniah: Late Birmingham
OL,4,Clegend first to receive city honour
OL,6,FHis best-known acting role was set in
OL,7,FBirmingham - appearing in 14 episodes
OL,8,Fof Peaky Blinders.
OL,10,FHe died in December 2023, at the age
OL,11,Fof 65, after being diagnosed with a
OL,12,Fbrain tumour.
OL,14,FBirmingham City Council has now
OL,15,Fapproved proposals to posthumously
OL,16,Fgive Zephaniah the City of Birmingham
OL,17,FMedal.
OL,19,FHe will be the first person to receive
OL,20,Fthe medal since it was created in
OL,21,FApril 2023.
