OL,3,CBenjamin Zephaniah: Late Birmingham
OL,4,Clegend first to receive city honour
OL,6,FCllr Sharon Thompson, deputy leader of
OL,7,Fthe council, described the writer as
OL,8,F"a proud Brummie and a man of
OL,9,Fcompassion who never forgot the
OL,10,Fcommunity that shaped him."
OL,12,FShe told a council meeting: "When
OL,13,FBenjamin died in December 2023, I made
OL,14,Fa promise to Benjamin's family that
OL,15,Fthis city would honour him in a
OL,16,Fsignificant way.
OL,18,F"It's fitting he is the first
OL,19,Frecipient of this medal because he
OL,20,Fspent his whole life breaking new
OL,21,Fground."
