OL,3,CBenjamin Zephaniah: Late Birmingham
OL,4,Clegend first to receive city honour
OL,6,FGiving a statement on behalf of the
OL,7,Ffamily this month, Zephaniah's brother
OL,8,FTippa Naphtali said: "Following
OL,9,FBenjamin's death in December 2023, his
OL,10,Ffamily were approached by many
OL,11,Findividuals, organisations and
OL,12,Finstitutions who wanted to stage
OL,13,Fevents or initiatives in his memory.
OL,15,F"In total, the family worked with over
OL,16,F45 such parties nationally in the year
OL,17,Ffollowing his passing.
