OL,4,Clegend first to receive city honour
OL,6,F"Right up to his death he remained
OL,7,Fcommitted to doing everything he could
OL,8,Fto promote and support Birmingham on a
OL,9,Fnational and international stage and
OL,10,Fwas passionate about giving the city
OL,11,Fthe recognition and national profile
OL,12,Fthat it deserves."
OL,14,FThe council has agreed it will now
OL,15,Fconsult Zephaniah's family to make
OL,16,Farrangements to award him with the
OL,17,Fmedal within the next year.
